          "type": "AI_AGENT",
          "valid": true,
          "settings": {
            "input": {
              "prompt": "You are a CRM relationship analyst. Analyze this contact's most recent email and determine their relationship status.\\n\\nCONTACT: {{cd1a069d-fe80-4ac3-9d23-5a5bf32a4ba1.currentItem.name.firstName}} {{cd1a069d-fe80-4ac3-9d23-5a5bf32a4ba1.currentItem.name.lastName}}\\nCOMPANY: {{cd1a069d-fe80-4ac3-9d23-5a5bf32a4ba1.currentItem.companyId}}\\nDAYS SINCE LAST EMAIL: {{de092d9f-41a0-4439-9a7b-49c242e707c6.lastContactDays}}\\nEMAIL DIRECTION: {{de092d9f-41a0-4439-9a7b-49c242e707c6.emailDirection}}\\nEMAIL SUBJECT: {{de092d9f-41a0-4439-9a7b-49c242e707c6.emailSubject}}\\nEMAIL BODY:\\n{{de092d9f-41a0-4439-9a7b-49c242e707c6.emailBody}}\\n\\nCLASSIFICATION RULES:\\n- ACTIVE: Engaged conversation within 30 days. Back-and-forth exchanges, meeting scheduling, project discussions, warm tone.\\n- COOLING: Was active but slowing down. 30-90 days since contact, or last email was a brief reply with no follow-up.\\n- AT_RISK: 90-180 days since contact, or last email shows disengagement (short replies, declined meetings, unsubscribe-like language).\\n- COLD: 180-365 days since contact. No meaningful engagement in the email content.\\n- DEAD: Over 365 days, OR email is automated/marketing/unsubscribe, OR no email found.\\n\\nRespond with ONLY valid JSON, no other text:\\n{\"relationshipStatus\": \"ACTIVE|COOLING|AT_RISK|COLD|DEAD\", \"aiSummary\": \"one sentence explaining your reasoning based on the email content\", \"confidence\": 0-100}",
